() Tj
T*
(We are committed to delivering your orders quickly and safely. This policy covers) Tj
T*
(everything you need to know about how we ship, the carriers we use, estimated) Tj
T*
(delivery windows, how to track your order, and what to do if something goes wrong.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(1. ORDER PROCESSING TIMES) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1.1 Standard Processing) Tj
T*
(All orders placed before 2:00 PM local warehouse time on a business day are processed) Tj
T*
(the same day. Orders placed after 2:00 PM or on weekends and public holidays are) Tj
T*
(processed on the next business day. Processing time refers to the time it takes us to) Tj
T*
(pick, pack, and hand off your order to a carrier ? it does not include transit time.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1.2 Extended Processing Windows) Tj
T*
(Certain items require additional processing time:) Tj
T*
(- Custom or personalized products: 3 to 5 business days) Tj
T*
(- Pre-order items: shipped on or after the stated release date) Tj
T*
(- Items marked "Ships in 5-7 business days": fulfilled from a secondary warehouse) Tj
T*
(- Large or heavy items requiring freight handling: up to 7 business days) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(During peak seasons \(major sales events, holidays from late November through) Tj
T*
(December\), processing times may extend by 1 to 3 business days. We will display an) Tj
T*
(estimated processing time on the product page and at checkout.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1.3 Order Confirmation) Tj
T*
(You will receive an order confirmation email immediately after purchase. Once your) Tj
T*
(order is handed to a carrier, you will receive a separate shipping confirmation email) Tj
T*
(with a tracking number and a link to track your package.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(2. DOMESTIC SHIPPING OPTIONS) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2.1 Standard Shipping) Tj
T*
(Estimated delivery: 5 to 7 business days after processing.) Tj
T*
(Available for all addresses within the continental United States, Alaska, Hawaii, and) Tj
T*
(U.S. territories \(Puerto Rico, Guam, U.S. Virgin Islands\). Free on orders over $49. A) Tj
T*
(flat fee of $5.99 applies to orders below $49.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2.2 Expedited Shipping) Tj
T*
(Estimated delivery: 2 to 3 business days after processing.) Tj
ET
