(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(3. INTERNATIONAL SHIPPING) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3.1 Countries We Ship To) Tj
T*
(We ship to over 80 countries worldwide. The full list is available at checkout when) Tj
T*
(you enter your delivery address. If your country is not listed, we currently do not) Tj
T*
(offer shipping there.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3.2 International Delivery Windows) Tj
T*
(- Canada and Mexico: 7 to 14 business days) Tj
T*
(- Europe \(EU and UK\): 10 to 18 business days) Tj
T*
(- Asia-Pacific: 14 to 21 business days) Tj
T*
(- Latin America: 14 to 25 business days) Tj
T*
(- Rest of World: 18 to 30 business days) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(These are estimates. Actual delivery times depend on customs clearance, local postal) Tj
T*
(infrastructure, and carrier capacity.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3.3 International Shipping Fees) Tj
T*
(Fees are calculated at checkout based on destination, package weight, and declared) Tj
T*
(value. A shipping quote is displayed before you confirm payment. Fees are non-) Tj
T*
(refundable once the shipment is dispatched.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
