(4.1 How to Track Your Order) Tj
T*
(Once your order ships, you will receive a tracking number by email. You can track) Tj
T*
(your order by:) Tj
T*
(- Clicking the tracking link in your shipping confirmation email) Tj
T*
(- Logging into your account and navigating to Order History) Tj
T*
(- Entering your tracking number on our website's Order Tracking page) Tj
T*
(- Using the carrier's website directly) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4.2 Tracking Updates) Tj
T*
(Tracking information may take up to 24 hours to appear after the carrier scans the) Tj
T*
(package. Tracking events are provided directly by the carrier and may not update in) Tj
T*
(real time during transit.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4.3 Tracking Not Updating) Tj
T*
(If your tracking information has not updated in more than 3 business days \(domestic\)) Tj
T*
(or 7 business days \(international\), contact our support team. We will open an) Tj
T*
(investigation with the carrier.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
