(7. DAMAGED, LOST, OR STOLEN PACKAGES) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7.1 Damaged in Transit) Tj
T*
(If your package arrives visibly damaged, please take photos of the outer packaging) Tj
T*
(and the item before unpacking further. Contact our support team within 7 days of) Tj
T*
(delivery with your order number and photos. We will arrange a replacement or refund) Tj
T*
(at no cost to you.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7.2 Lost Packages \(Domestic\)) Tj
T*
(If your tracking shows "delivered" but you have not received your package:) Tj
T*
(- Wait 24 hours ? packages are sometimes scanned before delivery) Tj
T*
(- Check with neighbors and building management) Tj
T*
(- Contact the carrier using your tracking number) Tj
T*
(If the package is still not found after these steps, contact us within 15 days of the) Tj
T*
(expected delivery date. We will file a claim with the carrier and issue a replacement) Tj
T*
(or refund pending investigation results.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
