T*
(We are not liable for packages confirmed as delivered to the correct address that are) Tj
T*
(subsequently stolen. We strongly recommend requiring a signature at delivery) Tj
T*
(\(available at checkout\) or shipping to a secure location. As a courtesy, we may offer) Tj
T*
(a one-time replacement at our discretion.) Tj
T*
() Tj
